Sentencas: In order to develop the new cathode materials suitable for intermediate and low temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT/LTSOFCs), LaNi1-xFexO3 (x = 0.4 - 0.8) (LNF) materials were synthesized using co-precipitation method.
Titulo: A new candidate as the cathode material for intermediate and low temperature SOFCs

Sentencas: Their structures and morphologies were investigated by XRD and SEM, and their electronic conductivities at different temperatures were measured by do four terminal method.
Titulo: A new candidate as the cathode material for intermediate and low temperature SOFCs

Sentencas: Fuel cells were fabricated to evaluate the electrochemical properties of the LNF materials as cathodes at different temperatures.
Titulo: A new candidate as the cathode material for intermediate and low temperature SOFCs

Sentencas: The performance of 450 - 497 mW center dot cm(-2) was obtained in the temperature region of 580 - 650 degrees C for the LaNi0.2Fe0.8O3 cathode, and of 209 - 227 mW center dot cm(-2) at 400 - 500 degrees C for the LaNi0.4Fe0.6O3.
Titulo: A new candidate as the cathode material for intermediate and low temperature SOFCs

Sentencas: The excellent fuel cell performances indicate that the LNF materials are good cathodes for IT/LTSOFCs.
Titulo: A new candidate as the cathode material for intermediate and low temperature SOFCs
